Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: A common language?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h3rv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 14 Oct 1979
The many differences between the American and English languages. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.